data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: Latest Media Handller is a plugin for MediaPortal 1.2 (or later). The purpose of the plugin is to deliver information about latest: * Pictures * Music Albums * My Video * TVSeries * My Films * Moving Pictures * MvCentral * Recordings to MediaPortal skins so that they can display things like latest movie title, poster and backdrops.
